{"tid":1915642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【奶共】明報已經將武漢肺炎改左做新冠肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-08T10:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T12:33:34.000Z","uid":78546,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff2abf859d25be6bfa980f0ca33f3a6a8b45244","tid":1915642,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"明報即時新聞緊跟中共主旋律，近日將所有新聞標題以及內文中的「武漢肺炎」改為「新冠肺炎」。<br />\n<br />\n浸大新聞系高級講師呂秉權：「新冠」是中共式爛中文，毫無語理可言。「武漢肺炎」就武漢肺炎，不用閃閃縮縮，諸多狡辯。<br />\n<br />\n聯絡明報<br />\n電郵：mingpao@mingpao.com / inews@mingpao.com<br />\n電話：2595 3111 / 9181 4676<br />\n<br />\n～～～<br />\n歡迎向我哋舉報，一齊監察香港中文。<br />\n<br />\n方法好簡單：<br />\n1）有圖有真相，最緊要影相。<br />\n2）Inbox張相俾香港中文監察。<br />\n3）一齊投訴投訴再投訴！！！<br />\n<br />\n課金支持：<a href=\"https://donorbox.org/hkclm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonorbox.org%2Fhkclm&d=W4F44tB2NhBwWjndCc5Bw9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=3f5ad547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://donorbox.org/hkclm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0U0OMny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0U0OMny.jpg&h=f7aef3be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d099a8ed124cafe513f4c24befb134030f58cc0","tid":1915642,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:12:20.000Z","msg":"支那真係好恐怖，首先改名撇走武漢，跟住再傳係美國佬放出黎，徹底推卸曬個責任"},{"pid":"33638efaf6a64b4efa39658609b7037797a908fd","tid":1915642,"uid":57532,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"跟住報道其他地方就黐住個地方名：美國新冠肺炎、日本新冠肺炎、南韓新冠肺炎&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebdf17b4a7e986dfd64baa1eda076fcd10c6b376","tid":1915642,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\nWuhan Virus</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c25552f7a5963604df04069d7f198d6d479972dc","tid":1